<chapter id="installing">

<title>Installing &MiKTeX;</title>

<para>You use the &BasicMiKTeXInstaller; to install &MiKTeX; on your
computer. You can download the installer from
the <ulink url="http://miktex.org/download">&MiKTeX; download
page</ulink>.
</para>

<para>Please read
<ulink url="http://miktex.org/howto/install-miktex">the installation
tutorial</ulink> for a step-to-step guide.</para>

